channel.title: Bone UN-Banker / Buryer
channel.description:
Hi, I am looking for a script that would open the bank and take out a full inventory of big bones then bury them. It should be fairly simple, but I know nothing about scripting for Aryan.
Incase anyone is wondering ... I bought about 4k big bones to put up my prayer lvl, but i don't want to sit there burying them all lol... :)
